***FIXED***
This is my take on Stormwind City in World of Warcraft for Counter-Strike:Source.  It isn't perfect, but you get the idea.  I was going to map all of stormwind, but all I have is the gates and the valley of heroes.  It's pretty full.  Created by: Reborn (Steam Account: Gamergman)  I have fixed most bugs, and added more detail.  I hope you like it!
